## Features

- Inbox list with user avatars and preview
- Dynamic chat window with send/receive logic
- Fin AI Copilot: Suggested prompts + hover tooltips
- Details panel: Assignee, Links, Attributes, etc.
- Responsive layout for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- AI message composer with edit/rephrase features
- Typing animations, scroll-to-bottom, toolbar toggles
- Optional dark mode toggle

